## EXAMPLES
# (unchanged + 2 new D11 examples)
- SAM Function with full DeploymentPreference (the standard skeleton):
    PredictFunction:
      Type: AWS::Serverless::Function
      DependsOn: PredictLogGroup
      Properties:
        FunctionName: !Sub accelya-predict-cancel-risk-${Learner}
        CodeUri: ../src/predict/
        Handler: handler.handler
        Runtime: python3.12
        MemorySize: 512
        Timeout: 45
        Tracing: Active
        Environment:
          Variables:
            ENDPOINT_NAME: !Sub accelya-cancel-risk-${Learner}
            CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD: '0.7'
        LoggingConfig:
          LogGroup: !Ref PredictLogGroup
        AutoPublishAlias: live
        DeploymentPreference:
          Type: Linear10PercentEvery1Minute
          Hooks:
            PreTraffic: !GetAtt PreTrafficHook.Arn
          Alarms:
            - !Ref IteratorAgeAlarm
            - !Ref BedrockThrottleAlarm
    PredictLogGroup:
      Type: AWS::Logs::LogGroup
      DeletionPolicy: Retain
      UpdateReplacePolicy: Retain
      Properties:
        LogGroupName: !Sub /aws/lambda/accelya-predict-cancel-risk-${Learner}
        RetentionInDays: 14

- OIDC trust policy (GitHub — correct, scoped):
    {
      "Version": "2012-10-17",
      "Statement": [{
        "Effect": "Allow",
        "Principal": { "Federated": "arn:aws:iam::<account>:oidc-provider/token.actions.githubusercontent.com" },
        "Action": "sts:AssumeRoleWithWebIdentity",
        "Condition": {
          "StringEquals": { "token.actions.githubusercontent.com:aud": "sts.amazonaws.com" },
          "StringLike":   { "token.actions.githubusercontent.com:sub": "repo:jaisingh-builds/accelya-agentic-aws:ref:refs/heads/module-11-*" }
        }
      }]
    }

- GitHub Actions OIDC job pattern (use this — NOT manual sts assume-role):
    jobs:
      deploy:
        runs-on: ubuntu-latest
        permissions:
          id-token: write     # MANDATORY — without this, no JWT is minted
          contents: read
        steps:
          - uses: actions/checkout@v4
          - uses: aws-actions/configure-aws-credentials@v4
            with:
              role-to-assume: ${{ secrets.AWS_OIDC_ROLE_ARN }}
              aws-region: ap-south-1
              role-session-name: gh-${{ github.run_id }}
          - run: aws sts get-caller-identity     # sanity check
          - run: sam deploy ...

